         <abstract id="aspace_632a6022bf2ab26ee454f898115451f3">This collection contains documents owned or written by Edward Augustus Anketell, 1864. Anketell lived from 1840-1917 and attended both Yale College and Yale Law School. This collection documents several classes and lectures, student life, Anketell's personal life, the New Haven landscape and buildings, and the Civil War.</abstract>
