      <bioghist id="aspace_4ed6211595ee962ebc7df671f46a9378">
         <head>Biographical / Historical</head>
         <p>Edward Augustus Anketell (1840-1913), was a member of the Yale College Class of 1864 and the Yale Law School Class of 1866. Anketell was a prominent New Haven attorney and secretary of his law school class.</p>
         <p>Biographical informatin obtained from donor.</p>
      </bioghist>
